es/YAAMAI/home.html Maimonides, a biography] \u2014 book by David Yellin and Israel Abrahams\n* [http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/maimonides Maimonides as a Philosopher]\n* [http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/maimonides-islamic The Influence of Islamic Thought on Maimonides]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090218232603/http://www.hoover.org/publications/policyreview/38243009.html \"The Moses of Cairo,\"] Article from ''Policy Review''\n* [http://www.neohasid.org/torah/rambam/ Rambam and the Earth: Maimonides as a Proto-Ecological Thinker]&nbsp;\u2013 reprint on neohasid.org from The Encyclopedia of Religion and Ecology\n* [http://faur.derushah.com/articlesbyhakhamjosefaur.html#anti Anti-Maimonidean Demons] by Jose Faur, describing the controversy surrounding Maimonides's works\n* David Yellin and Israel Abrahams, ''[http://penelope.uchicago.edu/Thayer/E/Gazetteer/People/Maimonides/YAAMAI/home.html Maimonides]'' (1903) (full text of a biography)\n* {{cite encyclopedia | editor = Thomas Hockey | display-editors = etal | author = Y. Tzvi Langermann | title=Maimonides: Ab\u016b \u02bfImr\u0101n M\u016bs\u0101 &#91;Moses&#93; ibn \u02bfUbayd All\u0101h &#91;Maym\u016bn&#93; al\u2010Qur\u1e6dub\u012b | encyclopedia = The Biographical Encyclopedia of Astronomers | publisher = Springer | year = 2007 | location = New York | pages = 726\u20137 | url=http://islamsci.mcgill.ca/RASI/BEA/Maimonides_BEA.htm | isbn=978-0-387-31022-0}} ([http://islamsci.mcgill.ca/RASI/BEA/Maimonides_BEA.pdf PDF version])\n* Maimonides at [http://intellectualencounters.org intellectualencounters.org]\n* {{cite book |last1=Kriesel |first1=Howard |title=Judaism as Philosophy: Studies in Maimonides and the Medieval Jewish Philosophers of Provence |date=2015 |publisher=[[Academic Studies Press]] |location=Boston |doi=10.2307/j.ctt21h4xpc |jstor=j.ctt21h4xpc|isbn=9781618117892 }} {{open access}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Friedberg |first1=Albert |title=Crafting the 613 Commandments: Maimonides on the Enumeration, Classification, and Formulation of the Scriptural Commandments |date=2013 |publisher=[[Academic Studies Press]] |location=Boston |doi=10.2307/j.ctt21h4wf8|jstor=j.ctt21h4wf8|isbn=9781618118486 }} {{open access}}\n*[https://groups.yahoo.com/neo/groups/maimonides/info Yahoo Maimonides Discussion Group]\n*''[https://www.maimonides-guide.com/ The Guide: An Explanatory Commentary on Each Chapter of Maimonides' Guide of The Perplexed]''  by&nbsp;Scott Michael Alexander (covers all of Book I, currently)\n\n;Maimonides's works\n* [http://www.chabad.org/library/article_cdo/aid/682956/jewish/Mishneh-Torah.htm Complete Mishneh Torah online, halakhic work of Maimonides]\n* [http://www.chabad.org/library/article_cdo/aid/940209/jewish/Sefer-Hamitzvot-Translation.htm Sefer Hamitzvot, English translation]\n* [http://www.torahforme.com/files/Rambam/ Oral Readings of Mishne Torah] \u2014 Free listening and Download, site also had classes in Maimonides's ''[[The Yemen Epistle|Iggereth Teiman]]''\n* [http://www.aish.com/spirituality/philosophy/Maimonides_13_Principles_-_Part_1_God_as_Creator.asp Maimonides 13 Principles]\n* [http://www.intellectualencounters.org/KotarApp/BrowseBooks.aspx?ExpandNodeID=2442$2443$2446&bAsImage=False Intellectual Encounters \u2013 Main Thinkers \u2013 Moses Maimonides], in [https://web.archive.org/web/20120415041817/http://www.intellectualencounters.org/ intellectualencounters.org]\n* [http://bodleian.thejewishmuseum.org/?p=21 Maimonides, Mishneh Torah, Autograph Draft], Egypt, {{circa}} 1180\n* [http://bodleian.thejewishmuseum.org/?p=15 Maimonides, Commentary on the Mishnah, Autograph Manuscript], Egypt, {{circa}} 1167\u201368\n\n;Texts by Maimonides\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080703012045/http://www.derushapublishing.com/siddur-mesorath-moshe.shtml Siddur Mesorath Moshe], a prayerbook based on the early Jewish liturgy as found in Maimonides's Mishne Tora\n* [http://www.mechon-mamre.org/e/e0000.htm Rambam's introduction to the Mishneh Torah 